name: product_information_extraction
description: Product Information Extraction deals with the extraction of product information based on an attribute from product title & product description
task_prefix:
Extract all important attribute name : attribute value pairs mentioned in the product title below and return the attribute name : attribute value pairs. All parts of the product title should be assigned to an attribute. 
 Desired format: <attribute name>: <attribute value> 
 <attribute name>: <attribute value>
